Package: IHW
Title: Independent Hypothesis Weighting
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: person("Nikos", "Ignatiadis", email = "nikos.ignatiadis01@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Modified Benjamini Hochberg like procedure which takes p--values and covariates
    (independent of the p--values under the Null) into account. This can increase power
    in a plethora of applications.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
